<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">無障礙功能</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents"><p class="p">
        The Unity desktop includes assistive technologies to support users with 
        various impairments and special needs, and to interact with common 
        assistive devices. Many accessibility features can be accessed from the 
        <span class="gui">Universal Access</span> section of <span class="gui">System Settings</span>.
      </p></div>
<div id="vision" class="sect"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">視覺障礙</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">失明</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-braille.html" title="以盲文閱讀螢幕">以盲文閱讀螢幕</a><span class="desc"> — 在盲文顯示機上使用 <span class="app">Orca</span> 螢幕閱讀器</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-screen-reader.html" title="大聲朗讀螢幕">大聲朗讀螢幕</a><span class="desc"> — 使用 <span class="app">Orca</span> 螢幕閱讀器來朗讀使用者介面。</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">低視力</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-font-size.html" title="改變螢幕上的文字大小">改變螢幕上的文字大小</a><span class="desc"> — 使用較大的字體，讓文字更容易閱讀。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-contrast.html" title="調整對比">調整對比</a><span class="desc"> — 將螢幕上的視窗和按鈕的鮮明度增加（或減少），比較容易觀看。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="keyboard-cursor-blink.html" title="讓鍵盤游標閃爍">讓鍵盤游標閃爍</a><span class="desc"> — 讓輸入點閃爍，並控制閃爍的快慢。</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
<div id="sound" class="sect"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">聽覺障礙</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents"><div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ul><li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-visualalert.html" title="為警示音效閃動螢幕">為警示音效閃動螢幕</a><span class="desc"> — 當播放警示音效時，啟用視覺警示閃動螢幕、視窗。</span>
</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div>
</div></div>
<div id="mobility" class="sect"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">行動障礙</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">滑鼠移動</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="mouse-mousekeys.html" title="Click and move mouse pointer using the keypad">Click and move mouse pointer using the keypad</a><span class="desc"> — Enable mouse keys to control the mouse with the keypad.</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="mouse-sensitivity.html" title="調整滑鼠與觸控板的速度">調整滑鼠與觸控板的速度</a><span class="desc"> — 改變使用滑鼠/觸控板時游標移動的速度。</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">點擊與拖曳</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-right-click.html" title="模擬滑鼠的右鍵點擊">模擬滑鼠的右鍵點擊</a><span class="desc"> — 將滑鼠左鍵按住不放來作右鍵點擊。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-dwellclick.html" title="用停駐來模擬點擊">用停駐來模擬點擊</a><span class="desc"> — 有了停駐點擊（替代點擊）功能，只要將滑鼠定住不動就可以完成點擊。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="mouse-doubleclick.html" title="調整滑鼠雙擊速度">調整滑鼠雙擊速度</a><span class="desc"> — 控制第二下點擊要多快才可以完成雙擊動作。</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">鍵盤使用</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="keyboard-osk.html" title="使用螢幕鍵盤">使用螢幕鍵盤</a><span class="desc"> — 使用螢幕上的鍵盤，用滑鼠點擊按鈕來輸入文字。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="keyboard-nav.html" title="鍵盤導覽">鍵盤導覽</a><span class="desc"> — 不需滑鼠即可使用應用程式與桌面。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-bouncekeys.html" title="開啟回鍵">開啟回鍵</a><span class="desc"> — 將同一按鍵的快速重續按鍵忽略。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-slowkeys.html" title="開啟遲緩按鍵">開啟遲緩按鍵</a><span class="desc"> — 從按下按鍵到螢幕出現該字之間插入延遲。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-stickykeys.html" title="開啟黏性特殊鍵">開啟黏性特殊鍵</a><span class="desc"> — 一次按一個鍵來輸入捷徑鍵，不用再同時按下所有鍵了。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="keyboard-repeat-keys.html" title="關閉按鍵重複輸入">關閉按鍵重複輸入</a><span class="desc"> — 設定讓鍵盤不要在按住一鍵時重複輸入，或是更改重複按鍵的延遲時間與速度。</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>
